Package avdta.network.link.cell

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cell
    This class represents a cell in the cell transmission model of a link (CTMLink).
    DLRCell
    This is an extension of Cell for dynamic lane reversal (see DLRCTMLink).
    DLREndCell  
    DLRLinkCell
    This is a regular cell for dynamic lane reversal links.
    DLRStartCell
    This type of Cell appears only at the start of a DLRCTMLink
    EndCell
    This type of Cell appears only at the end of a CTMLink.
    LinkCell
    This is a regular link cell, and appears between the start and end cells on a CTMLink.
    SharedTransitCell
    This class represents a cell in the cell transmission model of a dynamic transit lane link (SharedTransitCTMLink).
    SharedTransitEndCell
    This type of Cell appears only at the end of a SharedTransitCTMLink.
    SharedTransitLinkCell
    This is a regular link cell, and appears between the start and end cells on a SharedTransitCTMLink.
    SharedTransitStartCell
    This type of Cell appears only at the start of a SharedTransitCTMLink
    StartCell
    This type of Cell appears only at the start of a CTMLink
